          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma-ray spectra from separate foils were",
                "measured using a computerized gamma-spectroscopy",
                "system, CICERO-8K equipped with a HPGe detector in JINR",
                "The spectrometer was calibrated for gamma-ray energy",
                "using calibrated radionuclide sources of 133Ba",
                "and 152Eu."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "BCINT",
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "A target containing 7.7 g/cm**2  25 foils in the stack",
                "of vanadium was bombarded at a proton beam current of",
                "160 nanoAmperes approximately for 406 hours -during",
                "intermittent bombardment over a period of 4.5 years."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The total errors in the cross section were",
                "obtained by taking square roots of the sums of the",
                "squares of all the individual errors, like those in:",
                "  * the detection efficiency,",
                "  * counting geometry and statistics,",
                "  * attenuation corrections,",
                "  * irradiation and cooling times,",
                "  * proton beam monitoring,",
                "  * decay schemes,",
                "  * computer spectral integration, etc.",
                " The resulting total error  is thus partly systematic",
                "and amounts to between 15-20%. Authors assumed for the",
                "cross sections an error of 20%."
              ]
            }
          ],
